{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, \"held the object aloft and intoned\" was redacted to \"lifted an object and uttered\".",
    "Similarly, \"made motions in the air, making sounds and shaking their head\" was redacted to \"moved in the air, producing sound and motion\", further obfuscating the actions taken by the entities.",
    "In the fourth redaction, these changes are listed as Descriptions and Actions: Descriptions were made even vaguer, with specific details being replaced by more generalized terms.",
    "\"Gestured\" was changed to \"made movements,\" and \"performed an act\" replaced \"moved.\"",
    "Similarly, the action of \"observing\" was replaced with the more general term \"witnessing\"."
  ]
}